The paper deals with a beamforming strategy for directional frame timing synchronization in wideband millimeter-wave systems, which involves signal processing, communication theory, and network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
